    Greater Than Or Equal To Sign ≥

    Monadic Greater Than or Equal To Sign is not defined

    Dyadic Greater Than or Equal To Sign means

    Is Greater Or Equal To 

          1 2 3 ≥ 4 2 ¯1
0 1 1
      1 2 3 ≥ 2
0 1 1
